  "text": "Each AVA possesses a single Fixed-Viewpoint PanTilt-Zoom (FV-PTZ) camera [CITATION_1] : its projection center stays fixed irrespectively of any camera rotations and zoomings. An AVA can track the moving object as illustrated in Fig.1: 1. Generate a wide panoramic image of the scene; with the FV-PTZ camera, a wide panoramic image can be easily generated by mosaicing multiple images observed by changing pan, tilt and zoom parameters.",
